01:50:54.297 --> 01:51:00.297
Important parts to note here is that you're going to create new slides with level one or level two headers.

01:51:00.297 --> 01:51:03.297
So that'd be like pound pound heading.

01:51:03.297 --> 01:51:12.297
And then you can add content or list or images or codes within each of those pages and just fit them into whatever the overall structure of your page looks like.

01:51:12.297 --> 01:51:16.297
Again, if we use our fence divs, we can use that to create columns.

01:51:16.297 --> 01:51:25.297
So I might have some content on the left, more content, an additional list, and a paragraph of text that is important to hold on the left, but it's fun to include below the list.

01:51:25.297 --> 01:51:33.297
