01:51:53.297 --> 01:51:57.297
So four colons and then a .columns with an S.

01:51:57.297 --> 01:52:05.297
And then within it, each different column I'm creating, I'm just creating two here, will be its own fenced div with a .column class,

01:52:05.297 --> 01:52:10.297
and then an additional .fragment so they show up as I move through the presentation.

01:52:10.297 --> 01:52:18.297
