02:01:30.298 --> 02:01:42.298
And that's really what Cordo is trying to provide is a way of allowing colleagues in multiple languages to work together on the same project and not bump up into each other when they're trying to execute their code.

02:01:42.298 --> 02:01:48.298
So that's part of what projects and managing execution allow you to do.

02:01:48.298 --> 02:01:53.298
